<1ST_LINE>r a AM-Deaths 1stLd-Writethru a0801 11-30 0224</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Deaths, 1st Ld - Writethru, a0801,0228</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: ADDS Cafritz; A separate moved for the AMs as a0403 on
Cafritz.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Angela Aames</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WEST HILLS, Calif. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Angela Aames, 32, an actress who most
recently appeared as a fitness instructor in ``The Dom DeLuise
Show,'' died Sunday of unknown causes. An autopsy was being
conducted to determine the cause of death.
   Miss Aames had bit parts in several television shows and was the
recurring character of ``Honey'' in the ``B.J. And The Bear'' series.
   She had guest appearances in such shows as ``The Fall Guy,''
``Alice,'' ``Cheers,'' ``Hill Street Blues,'' ``Night Court.''
</TEXT>
<BYLINE>Gwendolyn Cafritz</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
